Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（學生食堂暑假期間休息）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}由於長期受到恐怖襲擊的民眾的情緒日益不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}由GGP指揮的反恐特種機動部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}通稱"白色Ride隊"的投入法在議會上高票通過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}至於其具體投入的時間  目前還正處於討論階段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}既然恐怖分子使用了機動性能優良的Rideback
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}我認為投入警用Ride作為對抗手段可謂是大勢所趨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}我們現在必須考慮的是如何防止恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱成這樣子  還真虧你能做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得我說過社團活動中止了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以命令我的 只有我所認可的那個男人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}"白色Ride"在裝備方面 與其說它是警用車輛 倒不如就說它是種兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}我憂慮的會不會因此 警方而軍隊化等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}謝謝您的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我騎著也沒能作出那樣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那孩子卻做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}我沒法隨心所欲操縱的那玩意兒卻讓初學者的琳給降伏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是個什麼玩意兒 Fuego
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道也沒關係 這和你們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒關係 我們不是Rideback部的夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我有權知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:49.74,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:49.74,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}极影&蔷薇园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:51.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:51.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:12.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:36.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
